WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.574 --> 00:00:13.574
 400gr Patent flour 

00:00:15.171 --> 00:00:20.171
 100g coarse semolina 

00:00:21.333 --> 00:00:26.333
 1 bag of instant yeast 

00:00:27.571 --> 00:00:32.571
 3/4 tablespoon salt 

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:46.640
 Add the 700ml lukewarm water little by little. 

00:00:47.594 --> 00:00:55.594
 Mix it another 5 minutes 

00:01:01.288 --> 00:01:06.288
 Let it rise for 45 minutes 

00:01:07.838 --> 00:01:12.838
 After 45 minutes you can stir the batter briefly 

00:01:14.874 --> 00:01:19.874
 Let the pan heat up 

00:01:24.496 --> 00:01:32.496
 Cool it under cold water and dry it with a cloth 

00:01:40.122 --> 00:01:48.120
 Immediately scoop the batter into the pan 

00:01:57.824 --> 00:02:05.820
 Put the fire on the highest setting 

00:02:15.968 --> 00:02:23.970
 When the batter is almost dried, set the heat to the lowest setting 

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:30.960
 When it is completely dry, let it turn golden brown on the bottom 

00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:36.300
 Spread olive oil or melted butter on it 

00:02:37.169 --> 00:02:45.170
 Repeat the steps 

